        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "But he stiffened his neck, and hardened his heart — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He added obstinacy and incorrigibleness to his sins.",
        "children": []
      },
